title: Jean Michel Jarre 1979-07-14 Place De La Concorde
description:
Here is a nice bootleg dvd. Check my account for more classic bootlegs.

Please enjoy, share with friends and please seed :)

Place De La Concorde was Jean Michel Jarre's first concert, held on July 14, 1979, celebrating the Bastille Day. One million spectators attended this concert, setting up a new record for Jean-Michel to the Guinness Book of Records. The concert was broadcast on TV by Eurovision. This DVD is made of this broadcast.
